        <div class="block text-block">
         <h3 class="block-header">
          Be Smart
          <span>
           About Safety
          </span>
         </h3>
         <div class="inner">
          <p>
           The
           <a href="be-smart-about-safety.html" rel="noopener" target="_blank">
            Be Smart About Safety
           </a>
           program is a proactive funding project that is focused on reducing potential loss in the areas of workersâ€™ compensation, general liability, employment, auto, and property. Funding opportunities are available!
          </p>
         </div>
        </div>
       </div>
       <div class="wrap">
        <div class="block text-block">
         <h3 class="block-header">
          Healthy Campus
          <span>
           Network
          </span>
         </h3>
         <div class="inner">
          <p>
           The
           <a href="https://healthycampus.ucsc.edu/" rel="noopener" target="_blank">
            Healthy Campus Network
           </a>
           initiative uses an integrative approach to health, guided by the core values of fostering a high level of wellness, encouraging personal responsibility, respecting diversity, and working to reduce health inequalities.
          </p>
         </div>
        </div>
       </div>
       <div class="wrap last">
        <div class="block text-block">
         <h3 class="block-header">
          Report Insurance
          <span>
           Claims
          </span>
         </h3>
         <div class="inner">
          <p>
           Please report claims as soon as possible. Failure to report a claim in a timely manner could affect insurance coverage.
          </p>
          <p>
           <a href="https://ucscforms.wufoo.com/forms/skk2kik1gxom1w/" rel="noopener" target="_blank">
            Auto
           </a>
          </p>
          <p>
           <a href="https://ucscforms.wufoo.com/forms/rbcc35p1v2p9v6/" rel="noopener" target="_blank">
            Property
           </a>
          </p>
